name: Sessions - Collect
description:
As a pro user
  I want to ccolect data from active sessions
  So I can perform operations on targets I have already pwned

steps.name: I have a user "TestUser"
The "TestUser" has a workspace called "sessions"
I am logged in as a Metasploit Pro user "TestUser"
I ready the "winxp" vm target
I goto the "sessions" project
I go to the module run page for "/exploit/windows/smb/ms08_067_netapi" in the "sessions" workspace
I fill in the module target field with the vm target address
I select "Bind" from the "Connection Type"
I click the "Run Module" button
I should see the console
I wait until the "Launching" message is visible
I wait for all the tasks to finish without errors
I should see the following text:
I click on the first "Sessions" link
I click on the "Collect" link
I should see the following text:
I click on the first "Sessions" link
I click on the first Active Session link
I should see the following text:
I click on the "Collect System Data" link
I click the "Collect System Data" button to submit input
I should see the console
I wait until the "Collecting from Session" message is visible
I wait for all the tasks to finish without errors
I click on the first "Sessions" link
I click on the first Active Session link
